# The LabMate remote (git@github.com:shiinayane/LabMate.git) tracks ONLY the docs/ folder.
#
# Layout of this git root (Docs/):
#   docs/      -> pushed to GitHub (LabMate implementation docs)
#   research/  -> local-only research notes, archive, application analysis (NEVER pushed)
#
# Allowlist strategy: ignore everything, then re-include docs/ only. Anything new dropped
# at the root is ignored by default, so local material can never be pushed by accident.
/*
!/.gitignore
!/docs/

# OS cruft (also inside docs/)
.DS_Store
